                                 Table "public.sessions"
     Column     |            Type             | Collation | Nullable |      Default       
----------------+-----------------------------+-----------+----------+--------------------
 id             | uuid                        |           | not null | uuid_generate_v4()
 user_id        | bigint                      |           | not null | 
 ip_address     | character varying(45)       |           |          | 
 user_agent     | text                        |           |          | 
 created_at     | timestamp without time zone |           | not null | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
 last_activity  | timestamp without time zone |           | not null | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
 expires_at     | timestamp without time zone |           | not null | 
 stay_logged_in | boolean                     |           |          | false
 is_active      | boolean                     |           |          | true
 logged_out_at  | timestamp without time zone |           |          | 
Indexes:
    "sessions_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "idx_sessions_active" btree (user_id) WHERE is_active = true
    "idx_sessions_expiry" btree (expires_at)
    "idx_sessions_user_id" btree (user_id)
Check constraints:
    "valid_expiry" CHECK (expires_at > created_at)
Foreign-key constraints:
    "sessions_user_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE

